<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id5a1994b9-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c" identifier="/us/usc/t29/s115"><num value="115">§ 115.</num><heading> Repeal of conflicting acts</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">All acts and parts of acts in conflict with the provisions of this chapter are repealed.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id5a1994ba-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c">(<ref href="/us/act/1932-03-23/ch90/s15">Mar. 23, 1932, ch. 90, § 15</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/47/73">47 Stat. 73</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
